Field Reports form should have the following input fields:

 Required Fields:

  - site_id - Site selector (references sites table)

  - report_type - Select dropdown:

    - Daily Operational Summary

    - Incident Report

    - Maintenance Log

    - Safety Observation

    - Equipment Check

    - Security Update

    - Visitor Log

    - Other

  - report_title_summary - Text input

  - report_content_full - Text area (rich text editor)

  Optional Fields (via junction tables):

  - Related ASICs - Multi-select of ASICs

  - Related Equipment - Multi-select of equipment

  - report_date - Date picker (default to current date if none selected)

  Auto-generated Fields:

  - report_id_display - Auto-generated unique ID

  - submission_timestamp - Auto-set on creation

  - last_modified_timestamp - Auto-updated

   - submitted_by_user_id - Auto-generated

'new list' form should have the following input fields:

 Required Fields:

  - list_name - Text input

  - site_id - Site selector (references sites table)

  - description - Text area (150 characters max)

  Optional Fields:

  - list_type - Select dropdown with options:

    - Tools Inventory

    - Shopping List

    - Master Task List (Template)

    - Safety Checklist

    - Maintenance Procedure

    - Contact List

    - Other

  - status - Select dropdown (default: "Active"):

    - Active

    - Archived

  - owner_user_id - User selector (references flrts_users)

  - is_master_sop_list - Checkbox (default: false)

'new task' form should have the following input fields:

Required Fields:

  - task_title - Text input

  - status - Select dropdown (default: "To Do"):

    - To Do

    - In Progress

    - Completed

    - Blocked

    - Cancelled

    - Reassigned 

  Optional Fields:

  - Reminder_time: Date and time picker (Can only pick future date and time)

  - Due_at - Date and time picker (Can only pick future date and time)

  - task_description_detailed - Text area

  - task_description_detailed - Text area

  - task_description_detailed - Text area

  - assigned_to_user_id - if none added, defaults to created_by_user_id

  - site_id - Site selector (references sites table)

  - related_field_report_id - Field report selector

  - due_date - Date picker - defaults to current data if no date selected

  - priority - Select dropdown:

    - High

    - Medium

    - Low

  - Add Sub-task button (with sub-task title input for each)

Auto-generated Fields:

  - task_id_display - Auto-generated unique ID

  - submission_timestamp - Auto-set on creation

  - last_modified_timestamp - Auto-updated

   - submitted_by_user_id - Auto-generated

